h of crazy debate analogies, formulas, and strategies she's picked up over the years. CVs Debating:  2016 - Overall Best Speaker, Semifinalist, International Human Rights Law Debate  - Overall Best Speaker, Finalist, PJ Debate Open  2015  - Quarterfinalist, World Universities Debate Championship Malaysia, ESL category  - Semifinalist, Benilde Intervarsities  - Quarterfinalist, Philippine Intercollegiate Debate Championship  2014 - Finalist, National Debate Championship  - Champion, Inter-Institutional Consortium Ethics Bowl  - Semifinalist, Manila Intervarsities - Quarterfinalist, Ateneo Intervarsities Adjudication:  - Philippine InterCollegiate Debating Championship 2016  - Borneo British Parliamentary Championship 2015  - 3rd Best Judge in Asia, United Asians Debating Championship – Thailand - Grand final judge, Asian British Parliamentary Championship 2015  - Grand final judge, The Great Gender Debates Malaysia, 2015  - Grand final judge, Malaysian National Intervarsity Debate Championship 2015  - Grand final judge, Hong Kong Debate Open 2015  - Grand final judge, KIDA Open, Seoul 2015 展開文藻英語辯論社分享了文藻英語辯論培訓坊 暨wsdc臺灣區選拔的照片 · 2016年12月22日 · 抓緊腳步點選報名連結報名吧!!文藻英語辯論培訓坊 暨wsdc臺灣區選拔 · 2016年12月21日 · 《冬至好消息》 雖然說昨天早鳥優惠已結束，但我們聽到了大家的心聲，決定重新開放早鳥優惠至聖誕節12/25！別再錯過這波優惠，快點選下麵連結，報名2017文藻辯論培訓坊吧！ 再次提醒大家，匯款完要記得填匯款確認單，此表單會在報名完成後寄到你的信箱，謝謝😊 報名錶單：http://bit.ly/2gLU3DZ... The early-bird registration ended yesterday, but we have received several requests for the extension of early-bird registration. Therefore, we have decided to extend this special offer until 12/25. Don't miss the chance again, click the link below and join us in the 2017 Wenzao debate workshop! Registration form: http://bit.ly/2gLU3DZ Reminder: Don't forget to complete the transfer confirmation form which will be sent to your e-mail once you finish the registration. Thank you so much 😊 ----- Introducing trainer- Mithrun Swaminathan. Mithrun is an experienced debater from Malaysia. These are his Debate CV's: - Asians quarterfi